# maximumRating

**Instance Property**

The maximum rating that the template displays.

## Declaration

```swift
var maximumRating: NSNumber? { get }
```

## Discussion

This property is an [doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/Foundation/NSNumber] that contains a value in the range of 1 to 5. The value is a whole number.

## Accessing the Item’s Attributes

- **rating**: The current rating that the template displays.
